Instructions for Platform Padawan:
- move your character left and right via 'a' & 'd' or left & right arrow keys
- hold down the spacebar to charge your force jump, hold down longer to build
the maximum charge to go further!
- collect the training droids within the allotted time, or you'll die!
- make sure to stay on the platforms, or you'll fall to your death!
- If you do die, you must start from the beginning!
- Make it all the way to the end to prove yourself a true Jedi!
